(firstQuint)Modified Pectoral Nerves Block Versus Serratus Plane Block in Major Breast Cancer Surgery.

 This study includes three groups.

 The first group will receive ultrasound-guided modified pectoral nerves block prior to induction of general anesthesia.

 The second one will receive ultrasound-guided serratus plane block prior to induction of general anesthesia.

 The third one will not receive any block preoperatively.

